                </p>
                <h3>How you can contact us</h3>
                <p>
                    The primary point of contact for all issues arising from this privacy notice, including exercising your rights described above is our Data Protection Officer.
                    The Data Protection Officer can be contacted in the following ways:
                </p>
                <h3>By email</h3>
